<p>
	So what are the properties of clary sage oil? Derived from the flowers and leaves of the plant medicinally known as salvia sclarea, clary sage oil is usually clear or light yellow in colour. It is known for its sweet, aromatic fragrance, which is frequently described as reminiscent of nuts, spices and/or herbs.</p>
<p>
